{"tid":1294684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大量警察16樣嚴重違規行為，持續更新……","createTime":"2019-07-07T22:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T03:53:21.000Z","uid":202464,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6acc8b6d13421b0379ed4ffc53d62023e86a3561","tid":1294684,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:44:39.000Z","msg":"2019年7月7日晚上到7月8日凌晨，香港警察嚴重失控。大量警察懷疑故意觸犯一系列警察通例，完全不受規管。數小時內，大量香港警察的粗暴語言及肢體動作被拍攝下來：<br />\n<br />\n1. 示威者整晚並無衝擊警方防線，和平地在彌敦道遊行，甚至有不少示威者跟沒參與示威的普羅市民同在行人路上。但警察一方面虛稱群眾非法集結，呼籲市民離開，任意封鎖街道，另一方面當群眾離開時，警方在多條離開路線，三面包抄市民，並主動用警棍攻擊他們，以致他們無法離開。警方整個晚上持續主動攻擊市民，示威者連基本的防衛衣物都沒配戴。<br />\n<br />\n2. 無法離開、和平而無衝擊動作的的市民並無反抗動作，但被警察壓在地上，打至頭破血流後被拘捕。路過且並無任何動作的市民，亦曾無故被十多名警察制伏及箍頸。有女途人只是拿著一瓶樽裝水站立，但無故被十數警察攻擊並壓在地上。<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察衝進正在營業的快餐店追打及拘捕市民，同時封鎖現場拒絕讓記者拍攝，故意阻止所有記者採訪拘捕情形。同樣情況在各處出現，警察多番公然拒絕讓記者進入拘捕行動的現場作採訪。<br />\n<br />\n4. 並無參與示威活動、在旺角一帶消費的大量市民，曾被揮舞警棍驅趕和被警察喝罵，並用長盾撞擊。<br />\n<br />\n5. 現場戴頭盔及配上防暴裝備的大量警察並無委任證，當被問及時，有警員曾高呼「警察執行職務係唔需要展示委任證」。<br />\n<br />\n6. 當市民喝止警員暴力攻擊時，有警員跟市民說「認撚住我呀」，及「隻揪呀」。<br />\n<br />\n7. 有警員在市民表示要離開現場時，拒絕讓對方離開，並說「我俾你玩了成晚」。<br />\n<br />\n8. 一些穿軍裝背心的警員有佩戴黃底或白底黑字，寫上警員編號的紙張，但部份同樣裝束的警員故意將紙張反轉，隱藏編號。<br />\n<br />\n9. 有示威者被帶上警車後，警車馬上關燈，亦有被拘捕者被帶上私家車後，車窗拉上窗簾。警方多番故意讓記者和市民看不見被捕者在車內情況。<br />\n<br />\n10. 當現場只剩下記者後，警察將記者們驅趕到黑布街，並喝罵他們「行得慢」，一直推撞，幾乎引致人踩人，亦有記者幾乎因此倒地。警察亦曾用警棍主動攻打記者。全晚所有記者多番被大量警員推撞。<br />\n<br />\n11. 譚文豪議員曾被持長盾警員推撞，並被防線警員叫他「收皮」。鄺俊宇議員也曾被大量警察指罵，並被警察叫「收皮」。區諾軒議員也曾被大量警察指罵和推撞。<br />\n<br />\n12. 警察多番以強力電筒直射記者臉部。<br />\n<br />\n13. 市民勸喻警方冷靜時，警方曾高呼「我無冷靜過」。<br />\n<br />\n14. 警察曾派代表跟傳媒說「今晚不會打啦，唔會有你們想見到的場面」。<br />\n<br />\n15. 警察清場後，數輛警車在行人安全島調頭，危害過路市民生命安危，警察趕走在安全島上等候過路市民，並讓警車繼續通過安全島調頭。<br />\n<br />\n16. 有離開戲院市民，在行人路上被警察任意給予警告，警方無法提供解釋但喝罵市民。"},{"pid":"f492555d76a3c68525fa628d2e4847d0acf4b453","tid":1294684,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:46:30.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55f8b4caadad44f05e72062495c61682b4bfbaf","tid":1294684,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:46:34.000Z","msg":"XGSA"},{"pid":"70317d23d5a36530503a3ddcaa1fa69c0993842f","tid":1294684,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:54:54.000Z","msg":"一哥起身未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce77e0e01935dd29edad228d821665b57aed6e3","tid":1294684,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:02:25.000Z","msg":"其實尋晚旺角係咪實施咗宵禁"},{"pid":"78553f64bfbdf0259d0af4baf8ef6695871e63c6","tid":1294684,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:05:17.000Z","msg":"想問尋晚警方保護左邊個市民?"},{"pid":"401bd957b1bb4dedea220f877873dfb416c54c36","tid":1294684,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問尋晚警方保護左邊個市民?</blockquote><br />\n保護左支那自由行、"},{"pid":"39b2cebef105142b507e577aafbfbb6b293a975d","tid":1294684,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3674be8d2001ccb12a95aac93418fb0828b019","tid":1294684,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c988785e5462be19adebd49581be783bc38e86c","tid":1294684,"uid":56239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%B2-%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=fe43e5dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=c8fb1fdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%B2-%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n長文。簡單講，警察由正常/正義部隊慢慢變成為所欲為嘅爛仔，入法庭之前已能搞到市民雞犬不寧。而家香港都正一步步接近緊警察國家。<br />\n<br />\n對抗以外，不如諗下有冇方法早啲搵到方案替代警察的日常功能？喺情況變成無可挽回之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔可以旨意哩啲人型物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9e3ffe45ad0c024d43e77ebc995e780168b17f","tid":1294684,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c988785e5462be19adebd49581be783bc38e86c","tid":1294684,"uid":56239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%B2-%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=fe43e5dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=c8fb1fdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%B2-%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n長文。簡單講，警察由正常/正義部隊慢慢變成為所欲為嘅爛仔，入法庭之前已能搞到市民雞犬不寧。而家香港都正一步步接近緊警察國家。<br />\n<br />\n對抗以外，不如諗下有冇方法早啲搵到方案替代警察的日常功能？喺情況變成無可挽回之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔可以旨意哩啲人型物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:44:16.000Z","msg":"但巿民本身冇執法權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1364f886adfd714acce00e171e8f9db56d2eccc4","tid":1294684,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"16. 有離開戲院市民，在行人路上被警察任意給予警告，警方無法提供解釋但喝罵市民。<br />\n<br />\n心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adde10df6a004b8eeab5079b870661a1705865bc","tid":1294684,"uid":268625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"如你想投訴警務人員，你可到任何一間警署或投訴警察報案中心提出，或登入警務處的電子報案室，遞交網上投訴表格。<br />\n<br />\n投訴警察報案中心<br />\n地址 : 香港灣仔軍器廠街3號堅偉樓附翼地下 <br />\n（中區警署側）<br />\n投訴熱線 : 2866 7700<br />\n傳真 : 2200 4460<br />\n2200 4461<br />\n2200 4462<br />\n辦公時間 :<br />\n星期一至五\t上午7:30 -- 下午6:30<br />\n星期六、日及公眾假期\t休息"},{"pid":"a489eab3929a9b1f2f5c700b62a7cf00ebff124c","tid":1294684,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"支持警察 畏槍自殺"},{"pid":"4043e3f30addc234bf5da0e39313fb7276893d4a","tid":1294684,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"支持警察 畏罪自殺"}]}